      <section xml:id="sec-bf-outcomes">
        <title>Basics of Functions</title>
        <introduction><p>Here are the assessment outcomes for Basics of Functions. There are multiple versions 
            of each outcome so that there are options for multiple semesters of assessments. This section is 
            divided into 4 outcomes:
            <ul>
              <li><p>Solving Quadratic Equations</p></li>
              <li><p>Forms of Lines</p></li>
              <li><p>The Difference Quotient and Piecewise Functions</p></li>
              <li><p>Transformations and Combinations of Functions</p></li>
            </ul></p></introduction>
